metadata.name: Natur  (I)
metadata.description:
Natur (I)  - 1/1 Abstract Landscape is inspired by the nature colors & mother earth itself. It is brought to life for art lovers who especially love green and who they are nature admirers.
With this collection I invite you to a meditative state in which you can discover new things each time  when you look into them.
Watching these sceneries may give you some peace and serenity. 

Acrylic painting digitally enhanced as 1/1 NFT.
Once this NFT sold, collector can watch the original piece burning to ashes. Video can be sent either as private message or could be made public on twitter.

6000x4000 px
385x577mm
Physical Painting: 33x43.2cm
Date of Creation :08/03/2022


Certification of authenticity can be provided upon request. 

Copyright by Silvia Anan 

With Love,
